    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >CRYING BOOTH is a compilation of five single player scenarios created by CRYING BOOTH. Game one through four are first person experiences with stealth, survival, and puzzle elements, while Game five is a side-scroller platformer.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2351740/extras/2e5b5bc5fd64e1b03f8ef536ec449614.avif?t=1748421299\" width=450 height=90 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Get sacrifices to revive a hanging man. Follow his direction or do as you please.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Use cover and be aware of sight lines as you take everyone out. </i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>Look</i></strong><i> out for ammo to help with long distance kills!</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2351740/extras/5a9df35435badcc524fdc6dccd9321db.avif?t=1748421299\" width=450 height=90 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>You are seeking revenge on someone who has wronged you. Play with fire and complete the ritual.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Eliminate anyone on your way and find a way to take him out.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Manage the small amount of ammo you have left.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2351740/extras/b3cefcaf7e4309bffdb67a925c436aec.avif?t=1748421299\" width=450 height=90 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>It's Halloween night and your friends are coming over to trick or treat. Collect as much candy as you can!</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Watch out for <strong>HIM</strong>.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2351740/extras/77e2131ff861367f259c2b0fe33a6a62.avif?t=1748421299\" width=450 height=90 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>You wandered into a carnival after hours, and ended up trapped in a tent.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Can you outlast them all?</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2351740/extras/e6dc6c3d80bbf7c88e740350f0d1c973.avif?t=1748421299\" width=450 height=90 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Walking home alone, but there are so many distractions.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Avoid <strong>everyone</strong> and find a way home.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>Gamepads are supported, but do not fully support all menus.</i></strong></p></li></ul>",
